title: Strata
blurb: The excavation showed that the fossilized plesiosaur had been holding a placard which read, 'End Nuclear Testing Now'. That was nothing unusual. But then came a discovery of something which did intrigue Kin Arad. A flat earth was something new ...

title: Babylon 5: The Scripts of J. Michael Straczynski, Vol. 9
blurb: • Into the Fire • Epiphanies • The Illusion of Truth • Atonement • Racing Mars • Lines of Communication • Conflicts of Interest • 51-page introduction and commentary, written exclusively for this volume. • 11 pages of the black & white photos from JMS's personal archives. • Full color back cover featuring a Peter Ledger concept art illustration of Delenn. • A peek at JMS's own original outline for one of the Babylon 5 novels.
